            "title": "日股收跌989點或2.77% 創逾半年收市新低",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國關稅拖低全球股市，日股明顯捱沽。日經平均指數收報34735點，挫989點或2.77%，創逾半年收市新低。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/Japan_Financial_Markets_25093057469522.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/Japan_Financial_Markets_25093057469522.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日經指數今早裂口低開684點，未幾即失守35000點關口，早段最低曾見34102點，暴瀉1623點，但在開市後半小時內跌幅已逐步收窄。</p>\n</div>",
